{{Finnish}}
Portto (noun)

A [[harlot]], [[whore]], or a female [[prostitute]].

Derived from Swedish "porto" which means [[fee]] or [[cost]], like "Portot betalad" on pre-paid mail envelopes. 

Finnish synonyms: [[huora]], [[ilotyttö]], [[prostituoitu]]

Usage notes: 

Almost never used about a male person, in which case it is REALLY obscene, and the situation can quickly become life-threatening.

Calling a child portto or any of its synonyms is also deeply obscene, and can be considered child abuse.